 KrixxKroxx – On The Low Krixxkroxx is a fast rising afro-drill artiste born on the 29th of August in Ajegunle area of Lagos state. He hails from Udi a vibrant town Enugu State.The upcoming artiste is the first born son of Mr & Mrs Ezechi, and also a fresh graduate of Computer Science  the prestigious University of Nigeria, Nsukka. Krixxkroxx real name Ezechi Christian Chukwunonso is a fast rising talent in the city of Enugu state and is indeed a budding talent to watch out for. Social media handles: IG@iam_Krixxkroxx The artiste’s music career kicked off far back in 2017 as a DJ and evolved to full tie music in 2021 when he finally released his famous debut single “Butt and Body” in May 2021 which was produced by Nameless. His first body of work, UFO, The EP which was released  September 2021 has garnered over fifty thousand streams across all major music streaming platforms and the “krixxkroxx” hashtag over 120k views on Tiktok. His latest single “Blood money” released December 2021 has about 15k streams. His new single “On the Low” drops on the 14th of January and promises to be another show stopper The song says no matter how much people urge you to stay lowkey, your light can never be hidden, it’s gonna shine through no matter what. DOWNLOAD AUDIO The post KrixxKroxx – On The Low appeared first on NotjustOk. Receive top breaking news, events, ideas, and more!